TOKEN "webhook" READ

DESCRIPTION >
    This pipe is used to ingest webhook events into Tinybird for services that support webhooks with JSON payloads. The Pipe endpoint will receive requests, store them in tinybird.pipe_stats_rt and then materialized to their corresponding target Data Sources.

    To configure the webhook use https://<tinybird-region-host>.tinybird.co/v0/pipes/webhook?token<your-tinybird-token>&service=<service-name>


NODE default_webhook
SQL >
    SELECT 1